name: Nippon Cargo Airlines 747-8KZF [JA18KZ] Takeoff from Tokyo Narita ᴴᴰ
description:
First time seeing Nippon Cargo! This marks the fourth 747-8F operator that I've filmed (the other three being Cathay Pacific Cargo, Cargolux, and AirBridgeCargo at YYC). JA18KZ, NCA's sixth 747-8F is seen here lifting off from Tokyo Narita's runway 16R in this short video. 

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
